Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.54,0:00:20.43,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}It's come to the point where I just want to hoard all your words
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.43,0:00:26.40,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Even the ramblings from your travels are treasures to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.40,0:00:29.58,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Whether I sketch or erase it's all torn away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.58,0:00:33.13,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}That's the price I pay for my awakening
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:38.69,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Or my daydream's tricking me and I'm still lost in the unknown
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.69,0:00:41.86,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Illuminated by the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.86,0:00:45.03,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Your figure casts a shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.03,0:00:48.16,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}And when that silhouette wavers slightly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:50.99,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}That happens to be my cue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,0:00:57.96,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}I wish this were fiction but slow motion is how it begins
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.27,0:01:03.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}If the visceral warmth and traces you left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.88,0:01:10.05,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Are protecting someone's future, I'll play the warrior
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.05,0:01:13.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Amidst pain and sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:16.60,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}I'll conquer my fears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:19.65,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}It's a paradox of life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:22.11,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}Or perhaps God's algorithm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.40,0:01:25.86,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}When our tactics overcome
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.86,0:01:30.62,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(150,150)}We'll be laughing
