Dialogue: 69,0:01:35.14,0:01:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kofune Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:37.08,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\bord7\c&HD1AD37&\alpha&H30&\blur7\3c&HD1AD37&}Original
