Dialogue: 69,0:01:38.79,0:01:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When were ya born?\NWho gave birth to ya?
Dialogue: 69,0:01:42.37,0:01:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, at the wake, Mother scanned Mio, and
Dialogue: 69,0:01:47.76,0:01:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,later that night,
Dialogue: 69,0:01:52.82,0:01:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born in a cave.
Dialogue: 69,0:01:56.84,0:01:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This "Mother" of yers.
Dialogue: 69,0:01:59.40,0:02:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she Haine in Shiori's form?
Dialogue: 69,0:02:02.59,0:02:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:06.09,0:02:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did ya cut the brakes on Mio's bike?
Dialogue: 69,0:02:08.88,0:02:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:09.73,0:02:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Were ya trying to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:14.28,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(914,318)\fscx123\fscy123\frz-12.58\fax0.23\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\b1\c&H120E0A&\blur1}N{\c&H120D09&}urse's {\c&H120D08&}Office
Dialogue: 69,0:02:12.73,0:02:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't matter if ya died or not.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:14.82,0:02:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought it would be easier if ya got hurt and had to go to the hospital.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:19.51,0:02:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Easier to kill Mio at the hospital and replace her, ya mean?
Dialogue: 69,0:02:24.27,0:02:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:25.58,0:02:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hishigata is a Shadow supporter, after all.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:28.80,0:02:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Were those Haine's orders?
Dialogue: 69,0:02:31.22,0:02:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:32.35,0:02:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to do it, but I failed.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:36.54,0:02:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea they were going to make a Shadow of Mio.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:41.70,0:02:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Tokiko.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:43.50,0:02:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea why I wanted to kill her anymore.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:48.20,0:02:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine created ya in order to search for Ushio's Shadow, correct?
Dialogue: 69,0:02:52.86,0:02:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,For the traitor, yes.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:55.06,0:02:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't copy people.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:57.24,0:02:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Can ya do the same?
Dialogue: 69,0:02:59.30,0:03:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two types of copying.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:01.88,0:03:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Transformation—replicating something with your own body.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:04.75,0:03:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And childbirth—splitting off a part of your body to create a new Shadow.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Childbirth...
Dialogue: 69,0:03:10.34,0:03:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Us "children" can only birth one human Shadow each.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:15.48,0:03:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Children?
Dialogue: 69,0:03:17.16,0:03:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine can give birth multiple times.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:19.22,0:03:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But her body is weak, so it's not easy for her.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:24.20,0:03:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The grand-children I create cannot give birth.{TLC}{コドモから生まれるマゴの代には\N分娩能力がない。}
