Dialogue: 69,0:03:40.49,0:03:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I only have six days left to live,
Dialogue: 69,0:03:43.02,0:03:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,yet I don't particularly care at the moment.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:46.29,0:03:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's about it, I suppose.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:48.81,0:03:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Shin.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:50.73,0:03:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything very useful.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:53.25,0:03:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's okay.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:54.86,0:03:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-There's nothing for ya to apologize for!
Dialogue: 69,0:03:57.89,0:04:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa, this is a Shadow yer talkin' to, Sou.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:00.64,0:04:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well... But—
Dialogue: 69,0:04:04.77,0:04:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou?
Dialogue: 69,0:04:07.04,0:04:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 69,0:04:08.52,0:04:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is throwing me off!
Dialogue: 69,0:04:10.62,0:04:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine needs to consume a large amount of people in order to recover.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:15.29,0:04:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She is likely creating an army of children for this purpose.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:18.37,0:04:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad and I were helping Haine to recover for my mom's sake.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:24.19,0:04:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We brought her food and stuff,
Dialogue: 69,0:04:26.73,0:04:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was all a lie.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:30.03,0:04:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They have a different goal in mind.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:34.25,0:04:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad knows everything, eh?
Dialogue: 69,0:04:37.38,0:04:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Friggin' jerk.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:39.00,0:04:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's okay with all of us dying?
Dialogue: 69,0:04:42.24,0:04:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 69,0:04:44.30,0:04:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot I'm still having trouble accepting.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:46.87,0:04:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems Dr. Hishigata knows what Haine's true plan is.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:51.35,0:04:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to be meeting him tonight at 10.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:57.22,0:04:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:58.51,0:05:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Our next objective is decided, then.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:00.70,0:05:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,To the Hishigata Clinic.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:04.17,0:05:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm bein' eaten alive!
Dialogue: 69,0:05:05.66,0:05:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So many mosquitoes here!
Dialogue: 69,0:05:08.18,0:05:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect Mio, please.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:11.64,0:05:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that an order?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:13.97,0:05:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,An order, huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:15.87,0:05:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it is.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:19.31,0:05:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin,
Dialogue: 69,0:05:21.15,0:05:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,are ya scared of me?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:22.99,0:05:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer really far away.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:24.71,0:05:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I'd be lying if I said I wasn't.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:28.31,0:05:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you realize how many times you've killed me?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:30.94,0:05:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But those were in different timelines.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:33.81,0:05:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I personally haven't killed anyone yet.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:37.79,0:05:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I ask ya a question now?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:40.30,0:05:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:43.18,0:05:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Did ya get a girlfriend in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:45.81,0:05:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl—
Dialogue: 69,0:05:45.81,0:05:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 69,0:05:47.62,0:05:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Whaddya think yer askin'?!
Dialogue: 69,0:05:50.23,0:05:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little suspicious when Shin slips outta his local accent from time to time.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:54.07,0:05:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ya think it's weird?
Dialogue: 69,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 69,0:05:57.51,0:06:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And people in Tokyo couldn't understand my Wakayama accent.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:00.56,0:06:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when in Rome, do as the Romans do.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:04.91,0:06:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was just a joke.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:08.10,0:06:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Have ya ever thought about why I don't call ya "big brother"?
Dialogue: 69,0:06:20.41,0:06:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I'll protect Mio like ya ordered.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:24.29,0:06:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're the only one who can really protect her, Shin.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:31.14,0:06:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She makes no sense! \NWhat's with her?!
Dialogue: 69,0:06:34.10,0:06:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's move it, Shin!
Dialogue: 69,0:06:35.55,0:06:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
