Dialogue: 69,0:06:51.98,0:06:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unlocked.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:56.04,0:06:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 69,0:06:58.02,0:07:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All of our stuff is gone.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:00.75,0:07:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Our rooms were empty too.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:03.71,0:07:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The desks, beds, closets—everything.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:07.95,0:07:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Nagumo, is this...
Dialogue: 69,0:07:10.33,0:07:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:11.97,0:07:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, I don't see any human-shaped stains.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:14.48,0:07:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Only furniture was erased.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:17.27,0:07:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps there was something here they didn't want found.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:21.26,0:07:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But the objects seem to have been erased haphazardly.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:24.45,0:07:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if they knew something here needed to be erased,
Dialogue: 69,0:07:28.33,0:07:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but they didn't know its location.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:30.06,0:07:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That is my impression.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:32.50,0:07:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to be Dad's work!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:34.73,0:07:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that he's not here is proof enough!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus Mom's missing.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on?!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:41.14,0:07:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:44.35,0:07:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So ya sensed a Shadow in the clinic, Ushio?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:47.78,0:07:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:48.91,0:07:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:50.24,0:07:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's yer deal?\NStop squeezin' so hard!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:52.58,0:07:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer cuttin' off the circulation!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:53.77,0:07:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are ya scared?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:54.54,0:07:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Of course I am!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:57.38,0:08:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate hospitals at night!
Dialogue: 69,0:08:01.48,0:08:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear something.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:10.88,0:08:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not working. So, this sound...
Dialogue: 69,0:08:13.64,0:08:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like something's caught in the basement door.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullet holes, huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:20.10,0:08:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There are traces of a fight.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:23.41,0:08:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:24.89,0:08:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shadow is going below us.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:27.29,0:08:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's in the basement?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:30.72,0:08:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The morgue.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:32.59,0:08:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The morgue?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:34.21,0:08:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:36.03,0:08:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The only body down there is yours from when Dad swapped it for the funeral.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:41.83,0:08:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 69,0:08:42.94,0:08:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to be scared if it's my own body, then.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that how it works?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:46.48,0:08:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear means your survival instincts are working correctly.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:51.38,0:08:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to be ashamed of.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:53.28,0:08:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadows are scarier than monsters.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:56.27,0:08:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Gird yourselves for what is to come.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:07.55,0:09:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Mom's wheelchair.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:09.92,0:09:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it doing here?
Dialogue: 69,0:09:12.03,0:09:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.74,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(601,324)\fscx77\fscy77\frz21.05\fnSchuboiseHandwrite\fsp2\b1\c&H5D4E32&\blur0.8}Morgue
Dialogue: 69,0:09:18.01,0:09:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Did ya see its face?
Dialogue: 69,0:09:19.74,0:09:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 69,0:09:39.44,0:09:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's empty.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:51.50,0:09:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is...
Dialogue: 69,0:09:53.04,0:09:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,this for real?
Dialogue: 69,0:09:54.80,0:09:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This was below the whole time?
Dialogue: 69,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:00.66,0:10:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Was Ushio's body here?
Dialogue: 69,0:10:03.31,0:10:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:04.60,0:10:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If Ushio could have scanned it, \Nshe would've been able to recover.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:09.24,0:10:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone must have realized that leaving it until tomorrow wouldn't be wise.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:17.72,0:10:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna retry?
Dialogue: 69,0:10:19.47,0:10:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we gotta keep moving.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:21.91,0:10:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to find Sou's parents.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:25.26,0:10:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:27.07,0:10:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Toki, what is this hall?
Dialogue: 69,0:10:29.83,0:10:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a path that connects to Hiruko's cave.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:32.65,0:10:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an entrance down here too?
Dialogue: 69,0:10:34.67,0:10:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd go through here to reach Haine's nest and bring her food.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:38.62,0:10:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a different route from the one under the old clinic.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:42.85,0:10:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can just barely sense a Shadow.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:45.91,0:10:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the one from earlier went through here.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:51.92,0:10:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay close, everyone.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:53.78,0:10:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming up ahead.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:12.43,0:11:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:22.79,title,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\c&HC0A038&\blur7}Summer Time Rendering
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.95,0:11:22.79,title,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}Summer Time Rendering
Dialogue: 69,0:11:18.95,0:11:19.33,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 69,0:11:20.06,0:11:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?!
Dialogue: 69,0:11:23.49,0:11:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! D-Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 69,0:11:25.96,0:11:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But yer Dad's being killed!
Dialogue: 69,0:11:32.46,0:11:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 69,0:11:34.23,0:11:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right, Sou.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:36.43,0:11:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring her back.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:44.62,0:11:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 69,0:11:52.89,0:11:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not breathing.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:10.67,0:12:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme take over!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:15.99,0:12:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:17.30,0:12:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ya die, dammit!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:19.76,0:12:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya don't get to go without answerin' fer anything!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:22.71,0:12:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't allow it, ya hear?!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:24.56,0:12:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up! Dammit, Dad!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:39.01,0:12:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou?
Dialogue: 69,0:12:41.73,0:12:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No more hiding things.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:44.23,0:12:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We're family, aren't we?
Dialogue: 69,0:12:46.70,0:12:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitose—
Dialogue: 69,0:12:48.61,0:12:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How's your mother?
Dialogue: 69,0:12:50.12,0:12:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I cut her link with Haine.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:52.53,0:12:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She should wake up in a bit.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:55.32,0:12:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:56.92,0:13:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already reached this place.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:02.56,0:13:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Haine...
Dialogue: 69,0:13:05.92,0:13:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,must've thought I'd tell you everything.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:09.26,0:13:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in hiding things.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:11.13,0:13:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have to do is scan ya, after all.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:14.89,0:13:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokiko, kill them.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:17.74,0:13:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 69,0:13:18.62,0:13:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 69,0:13:20.85,0:13:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do, Haine will trust me again.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:25.98,0:13:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer wrong, Dad.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:28.09,0:13:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't happen.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:30.01,0:13:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shadows have no intention of keeping their promise to us.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:35.47,0:13:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You disappoint me, Tokiko.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:39.96,0:13:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back, Sou!
Dialogue: 69,0:13:41.44,0:13:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Your gun's too close!
Dialogue: 69,0:13:51.15,0:13:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc—
Dialogue: 69,0:13:54.46,0:13:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What... the hell?
Dialogue: 69,0:13:59.70,0:14:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 69,0:14:02.55,0:14:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to disappoint.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:05.48,0:14:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Shin and them will be okay.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:08.70,0:14:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Ushio and Miss Nagumo are there.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:13.90,0:14:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't forget about Shadow Mio.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:15.92,0:14:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm worried about the most.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:18.00,0:14:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't trust her.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:20.90,0:14:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised ya let her copy ya, Tokiko.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:24.93,0:14:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,When a Shadow copies someone, they get to see everything.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:28.99,0:14:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Body and soul, right?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:31.71,0:14:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:32.90,0:14:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted her to see the deepest parts of me.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:36.79,0:14:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Geez!
Dialogue: 69,0:14:37.95,0:14:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How can ya say that with a straight face?!
Dialogue: 69,0:14:42.61,0:14:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hide anything anymore.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:48.07,0:14:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio!
Dialogue: 69,0:14:50.63,0:14:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do ya trust me a little now?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:54.32,0:14:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you saved us.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:57.49,0:14:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:59.04,0:15:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and copy me if ya need proof.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:05.47,0:15:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna know what's in yer heart, Shin.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:10.02,0:15:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:11.49,0:15:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya shot Tokiko!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:13.01,0:15:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How the hell could ya do something like that?!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:16.37,0:15:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:17.35,0:15:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya bastard!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:19.08,0:15:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What do ya think human life is?!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:21.84,0:15:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill...
Dialogue: 69,0:15:25.24,0:15:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't ya a doctor, Dad?
Dialogue: 69,0:15:27.82,0:15:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A doctor ain't supposed to be talkin' about killing people!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:31.24,0:15:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:36.26,0:15:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Not gonna talk now, huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:15:38.85,0:15:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:40.80,0:15:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it, Mio.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:52.30,0:15:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't copy him.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:53.94,0:15:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He has immunity.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:56.79,0:15:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:58.08,0:15:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we just have to make you talk.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:59.14,0:15:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:00.27,0:16:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That shouldn't be!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:01.88,0:16:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't copy me?!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:04.90,0:16:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A Shadow of you was made and then died.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:10.20,0:16:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,People in that situation gain an immunity, and they can't be copied again.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:15.31,0:16:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Impossible!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:17.27,0:16:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't create a Shadow anymore?
Dialogue: 69,0:16:22.88,0:16:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:29.18,0:16:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc?
Dialogue: 69,0:16:30.43,0:16:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitose...
Dialogue: 69,0:16:32.58,0:16:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... why did I...
Dialogue: 69,0:16:39.54,0:16:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Negoro.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:44.83,0:16:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I will be taking my leave.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:48.92,0:16:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already completed my primary objective.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:54.86,0:16:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She's out of range!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:56.40,0:16:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I have a message for you from Shide.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:59.59,0:17:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Hishigata family has served us well.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:03.52,0:17:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But that is at an end.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:06.04,0:17:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work."
Dialogue: 69,0:17:08.80,0:17:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I also have a message for Ajiro Shinpei.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:12.11,0:17:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"It would appear you survived somehow.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:14.80,0:17:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an annoying cockroach.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:17.38,0:17:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet, you are powerless to stop us.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:20.18,0:17:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything will be over in two days."
Dialogue: 69,0:17:23.71,0:17:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, ya jerk!
Dialogue: 69,0:17:24.98,0:17:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 69,0:17:29.86,0:17:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya don't have to chase her.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:31.45,0:17:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 69,0:17:33.27,0:17:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She was using yer body as bait to lure us in.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:37.47,0:17:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She purposefully told us the time limit to provoke us.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:42.01,0:17:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over if we take the bait.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:43.46,0:17:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Shinpei!
Dialogue: 69,0:17:45.18,0:17:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so frustrating!
Dialogue: 69,0:17:46.67,0:17:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shadow we saw earlier in the hall was her!
Dialogue: 69,0:17:50.61,0:17:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Sis.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:53.03,0:17:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin is the one feeling the most frustrated.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:57.90,0:18:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya can't just act on instinct and expect things to work out.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:04.82,0:18:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Anger, frustration—
Dialogue: 69,0:18:07.07,0:18:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,View them objectively, and they become weapons.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:11.12,0:18:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei...
Dialogue: 69,0:18:13.24,0:18:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hishigata, is there any point in staying silent now?
Dialogue: 69,0:18:18.85,0:18:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter...
Dialogue: 69,0:18:21.67,0:18:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the real Tokiko here.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:33.61,0:18:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you awake?
Dialogue: 69,0:18:36.75,0:18:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sei.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:38.45,0:18:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where am I?
Dialogue: 69,0:18:43.71,0:18:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitose, I'm going to show ya my memories just like I've done to the doctor.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:51.89,0:18:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Chitose.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:54.11,0:18:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sou's mom had no idea she was a Shadow.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:59.91,0:19:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nor of how she was created.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:02.94,0:19:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're trying to stop the ritual.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:07.05,0:19:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But is killing Haine really the right decision?
Dialogue: 69,0:19:11.35,0:19:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 69,0:19:12.84,0:19:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing Haine means all Shadows will die!
Dialogue: 69,0:19:16.93,0:19:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you'll be killing your Ushio as well!
Dialogue: 69,0:19:26.53,0:19:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio...
Dialogue: 69,0:19:28.30,0:19:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, it's fine!
Dialogue: 69,0:19:30.14,0:19:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to die two days ago, anyway.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:32.96,0:19:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Living this long is just lucky.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:36.16,0:19:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I'm in bonus time, y'know?
Dialogue: 69,0:19:38.74,0:19:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I can use this time to save everyone, I want to.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:43.12,0:19:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So defeating Haine will solve everything?
Dialogue: 69,0:19:46.52,0:19:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good to hear!
Dialogue: 69,0:19:48.63,0:19:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll gladly take her down!
Dialogue: 69,0:19:53.20,0:19:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's right.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:54.58,0:19:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm ashamed of myself for hesitating.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:57.78,0:19:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 69,0:19:58.94,0:19:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:00.73,0:20:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hishigata.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:02.23,0:20:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Haine trying to do by reviving?
Dialogue: 69,0:20:06.80,0:20:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She only wishes to return home.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:11.44,0:20:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To her hometown, across the vast, deep ocean.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:19.18,0:20:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Creatures of this world cannot reach it.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:23.67,0:20:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only possible for Shadows.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:26.25,0:20:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Haine's only going to bring Shadows with her.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:29.80,0:20:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The family that she hand-picked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:38.59,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}All traces of you vanished into the sea breeze
Dialogue: 69,0:20:33.30,0:20:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That can't be!
Dialogue: 69,0:20:35.01,0:20:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible if her power returns, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:43.45,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}But even now I still see visions of you
Dialogue: 69,0:20:39.30,0:20:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an eternal country where time doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:42.60,0:20:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitose and I were supposed to become Shadows and live there forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:51.31,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}In reality I only have vivid memories
Dialogue: 69,0:20:48.15,0:20:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the end, Sou and Tokiko were going to become Shadows too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.31,0:20:56.26,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}To play in my head over and over again
Dialogue: 69,0:20:53.01,0:20:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why ya don't care if we die?!
Dialogue: 69,0:20:55.77,0:20:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How selfish can ya be?!
Dialogue: 69,0:20:58.48,0:20:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Are ya stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:01.64,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}Even if it's all just a lie
Dialogue: 69,0:20:59.99,0:21:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All this for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.64,0:21:05.30,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}Please be close by my side
Dialogue: 69,0:21:02.35,0:21:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so selfish and self-absorbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:08.41,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}Right next to me
Dialogue: 69,0:21:06.22,0:21:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do with ya.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:10.36,0:21:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank ya for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:14.63,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}I fell for you before too long
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.63,0:21:18.38,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}But time alone was what progressed
Dialogue: 69,0:21:17.07,0:21:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitose...
Dialogue: 69,0:21:18.38,0:21:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But we must end this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:22.87,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}I wanna go back
Dialogue: 69,0:21:21.64,0:21:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou, Tokiko.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:23.87,0:21:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to watch so much of yer lives.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:26.57,0:21:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:32.03,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}I've listened to my share of heartbreak songs
Dialogue: 69,0:21:28.89,0:21:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitose, wait!
Dialogue: 69,0:21:30.97,0:21:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you die, I'll have no reason to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:39.69,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}Spending my days torn up and crying but now
Dialogue: 69,0:21:34.56,0:21:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, ya have yer children.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:38.66,0:21:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And ya have the islanders that depend on ya too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:42.34,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}I want to move on
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:47.24,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}I shouldn't act tough and just finally be
Dialogue: 69,0:21:43.49,0:21:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei is correct.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:45.58,0:21:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over just yet.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:47.71,0:21:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya can still make things right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:50.55,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}True to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:56.49,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(200,200)}But it's too late for that
Dialogue: 69,0:22:05.60,0:22:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's in there?
Dialogue: 69,0:22:09.97,0:22:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The patient records Tokiko and I hid.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:14.50,0:22:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I diagnosed everyone here with Capgras delusion.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:17.64,0:22:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The shadow sickness, endemic to this island.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:21.49,0:22:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But the truth is that it's actually a list of Haine's food.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:27.60,0:22:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:29.41,0:22:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your parents' name are in here too.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:31.61,0:22:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mom and Dad—their boat sank during an expedition.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:36.92,0:22:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an accident.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:38.85,0:22:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They discovered Hiruko cave and were going to go public.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:43.83,0:22:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So they were killed.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:45.92,0:22:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It was made to look like an accident.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:47.93,0:22:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shide killed them, and I replaced the bodies and transported them to Haine.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:54.14,0:22:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:55.73,0:22:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Ya think that's all ya need to—
Dialogue: 69,0:22:57.99,0:23:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do ya know Shide's real identity?
Dialogue: 69,0:23:02.11,0:23:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 69,0:23:03.55,0:23:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at this photo.
Dialogue: 69,0:23:06.01,0:23:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shide is Haine's guardian and the first child she ever gave birth to.
Dialogue: 69,0:23:12.04,0:23:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,His original name was Hishigata Shidehiko.
Dialogue: 69,0:23:18.81,0:23:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The founder of the Hishigata Clinic, as well as its first director.
Dialogue: 69,0:23:25.93,0:23:26.15,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Preview}
